The teacher gave the task to write an essay on the topic "How I spent the day." Everything was written, passed for verification, Mary checked the bath, the next day, Vovochka's parents were called to school:
- Look at what your son wrote.
- Got up, washed, went to the toilet, wiped x%y, went to school, came, wiped x%y, had lunch, went for a walk, came from a party, wiped x%y.
Father:
- That's how I work in the police department, they very often write the word x%y in chalk on our door.
